works.description:
The album, in Maria Larsson's Gallery,  
named Exclusive Knitted Toy Pattern, contains 57 scanned images taken from
 
the patterns for knitted toys published in Simply Knitting and Woman's  
Weekly magazines. The quality of each scan is such that, by downloading
the  
images, the whole pattern can be illegally obtained. This infringes Alan's
 
copyright. The url of the album is below.
